    "updated_at": "2023-06-20T04:20:16Z",
    "body": "Facing this too, it occurs when copy pasted, any command from history or edited commands too.  This makes editing and executing a previously done command cumbersome since additional characters get added to it. \r\n\r\nMy only workaround right now is to copy the command into some other editor to edit,then bring it back to shell to use. \r\n\r\nUsing zsh on MacOS",
